      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Dablink|&quot;Auschwitz&quot; and &quot;Auschwitz-Birkenau&quot; redirect here. For the town, see [[Oświęcim]]. Distinguish from [[Austerlitz]]. Or see [[Auschwitz (disambiguation)]]}}
