      <text xml:space="preserve">{{About|the ancient Greek playwright}}

{{Infobox person
|name   = Aeschylus
|image     = Aischylos Büste.jpg
|caption  = Bust of Aeschylus&lt;br /&gt; from the [[Capitoline Museums]], [[Rome]]
|birth_date  = c. 525 BC/524 BC
|birth_place = [[Eleusis]]
|death_date  = c. 456 BC
|death_place = [[Sicily]]
|occupation     = Playwright and Soldier
